                    <span class="text-lg">Autoresponsabilidad</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Principios card -->
            <div class="card-container group">
              <div class="card-header relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-primary"></div>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='40' height='40' viewBox='0 0 40 40' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='%23fff' fill-opacity='0.05' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cpath d='M0 38.59l2.83-2.83 1.41 1.41L1.41 40H0v-1.41zM0 20.01l20-20 1.41 1.41L1.41 21.42H0v-1.41zM20 1.41l18.59 18.59H40V21.41L20 1.41zM30 10.01l10-10V1.41L29.42 12.01 30 12.6z' /%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E')] opacity-20"></div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white relative z-10 flex items-center">
                  <span class="inline-block w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  Principios Metodología EXCELSA
                </h2>
              </div>
              
              <div class="p-8">
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-start text-gray-800">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-primary flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span>Todo es posible</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start text-gray-800">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-primary flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span>Dentro de nosotros está toda la capacidad</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start text-gray-800">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-primary flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span>Todo resultado es mejorable</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start text-gray-800">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-primary flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span>El amor es vida y esencia de la existencia</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start text-gray-800">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-primary flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span>La paz es la madre de la sanación</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start text-gray-800">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-primary flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span>La alegría es el motor</span>
